txt.en: 'Knowledge is power, and the warrior that studies the battles of the past and the tendencies of his enemy greatly increases his chances of winning the battle. There is a small building in the back of town that, if rebuilt, we can outfit as a library and fill with books and scrolls that will allow our Rohirrim to gain the edge in battle.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
